            "title": "RabbitMQ主要工作模式",
            "date_published": "2020-12-01T09:15:01.800Z",
            "content_html": "<p>MQ 全称 Message Queue（消息队列），是在消息的传输过程中保存消息的容器。多用于分布式系统之间进行通信。<a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20201201171613531.png\" alt=\"image-20201201171613531\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201201171613531.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20201201171644352.png\" alt=\"image-20201201171644352\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201201171644352.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20201201171711864.png\" alt=\"image-20201201171711864\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201201171711864.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20201201171736965.png\" alt=\"image-20201201171736965\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201201171736965.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20201201171811299.png\" alt=\"image-20201201171811299\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201201171811299.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n",
